                <note rend="inline" type="source">817.1051/264: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Eberhardt</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-02-21T17:00:00-05:45"
                            >February 21, 1929—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 7:35 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>53. The guardia agreement with the amendments described in my telegram 52,
                    February 21, noon, has been signed by the President.</p>
                <p>Congress went into recess today for the purpose of studying the budget. It will
                    reconvene on March 5th for its two final sessions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Eberhardt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
